    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We present the first described case of acute disseminated encephalomyelitis (ADEM) in a COVID-19 patient. The clinical features with head CT and brain MRI changes were described. Our described case is an atypical presentation of the novel coronavirus in a young patient and is illustrative of the possible approaches to explore the treatable differential etiologies.</jats:p>",
